│ **2. Deconstruct the IR and the Problem**                                                                                    │
│                                                                                                                              │
│ The provided LLVM IR has a loop with a peculiar control flow structure:                                                      │
│ ```llvm                                                                                                                      │
│ loop.header:                                                                                                                 │
│   ...                                                                                                                        │
│   br i1 true, label %loop.latch, label %else                                                                                 │
│                                                                                                                              │
│ else:                                             ; (unreachable)                                                            │
│   %div.i = udiv i64 99, %d                                                                                                   │
│   br label %loop.latch                                                                                                       │
│                                                                                                                              │
│ loop.latch:                                                                                                                  │
│   %retval.0.i = phi i64 [ %div.i, %else ], [ 0, %loop.header ]                                                               │
│   ...                                                                                                                        │
│ ```                                                                                                                          │
│ The `br i1 true` makes the `%else` block unreachable. Consequently, the `udiv` instruction `%div.i` is never executed, and   │
│ the PHI node `%retval.0.i` will always receive the value `0`.                                                                │
│                                                                                                                              │
│ The loop vectorizer, however, analyzes the control flow graph as it is. It sees a diamond structure inside the loop and      │
│ creates a `VPBlendRecipe` for the PHI node `%retval.0.i`. The `udiv` instruction `%div.i` is one of the inputs to this       │
